mse version: 2.0.0
game: magic
short name: Sci-Fi
full name: InvertedVertex's Sci-Fi Mainframe
icon: card-sample.png
installer group: magic/m15 style/normal cards
position hint: 052

version: 2024-05-30
depends on:
	package: magic.mse-game
	version: 2020-04-25
depends on:
	package: magic-default-image.mse-include
	version: 2007-09-23
depends on:
	package: magic-modules.mse-include
	version: 2024-10-01
depends on:
	package: magic-mana-large.mse-symbol-font
	version: 2007-09-23
depends on:
	package: magic-mana-small.mse-symbol-font
	version: 2007-09-23

card width: 375
card height: 523
card dpi: 150
##### Flavor bar image by SirnightNano
##### Ancestral generic mana by ancestral
##### Nyx crowns by Angelus
##### Companion crowns, nyx extensions, DOM FNM frame, THB fullart lands by silverback_ape
##### PUMA by kebelqwa and cajun
